olve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors?download=true)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`  \n\n---\n\n\n## 🆙 Load Upscale Model  \n\n### Download 4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth mode from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Akumetsu971/SD_Anime_Futuristic_Armor/resolve/main/4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth?download=true)  \n\n**Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/upscale_models`\n\n---\n\n## 📚 Resources  \n🎥 **Tutorials:** [Pixaroma YouTube Channel](https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma)  \n💬 **Community Discord:** [Join Here](https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3)\n\nLearn more about Kontext model on [Comfy.org](https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/flux/flux-1-kontext-dev) and [blf.ai](https://bfl.ai/models/flux-kontext)\n\nLearn how to prompt for Flux Kontext [HERE](https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/flux/flux-1-kontext-dev#flux-kontext-prompt-techniques)\n\nLearn more about Nunchaku [HERE](https://github.com/mit-han-lab/ComfyUI-nunchaku)\n"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":203,"type":"LoadImage","pos":[-644.8355712890625,767.5952758789062],"size":[330.5078430175781,437.6168212890625],"flags":{},"order":14,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"image","name":"image","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"image"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"choose file to upload","name":"upload","type":"IMAGEUPLOAD","widget":{"name":"upload"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"IMAGE","name":"IMAGE","type":"IMAGE","links":[260]},{"localized_name":"MASK","name":"MASK","type":"MASK","links":null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.42","Node name for S&R":"LoadImage","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"version":"7.3","input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["Nunchaku Flux 1 Kontext Dev - Tshirt Try-on Input 1.png","image"]},{"id":233,"type":"LoadImage","pos":[-644.8355712890625,1297.134765625],"size":[330.5078430175781,437.6168212890625],"flags":{},"order":15,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"image","name":"image","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"image"},"link":null},{"localiz